<subSubSection id="64F788CF2E28F64BEADB81166951CC4C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="comments">
<paragraph id="6B875B56198B7AA7F47FDFEDF449F78A" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="38085163E0E4CFE4765D51031EF8F48B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">This species is newly reported from Guangxi, indicating that it is probably very broadly distributed in the low forested hills of southeastern China. The specimens from wet rocks in a forested river valley probably dropped when disturbed from overhanging coarse woody debris.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
